HEADWORD: Epanorthosis
<hw>Ep`an*or*tho"sis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
Gr. <?/; <grk>'epi`</grk> + <?/ to set right again; <?/ again + <?/ to
